      "text": "When Thou__ didst de-scend to death, O Life Im-mor--tal, then didst Thou slay Ha-des with the light-ning of Thy Di-vin-i-ty. And when Thou didst al-so raise the dead out of the neth--er-most depths, all the Pow-ers in the Heav-ens cried____ out: O Life-giv-er, Christ our God, glo-ry be___ to Thee. \n\nglo-ry be__ to Thee.___"
